item.title: Fisher & Paykel
item.description: From Distributed Denial of Secrets RELEASE Fisher & Paykel Over 30 gigabytes hacked from Fisher & Paykel, a major appliance manufacturer which is a subsidiary of home appliance manufacturer Haier, based in East Tamaki, New Zealand. DATASET DETAILS COUNTRIES New Zealand, Italy, United States TYPE Hack SOURCE Nefilim FILE SIZE 31 GB DOWNLOADS (How to Request Access) MORE REFERENCES EDITOR NOTES Over 30 gigabytes hacked from Fisher & Paykel, a major appliance manufacturer which is a subsidiary of home appliance manufacturer Haier, based in East Tamaki, New Zealand.
